.name
MailMerge
.author
Andrew Martin
SciTech Software 
.version
1.0
.description
A utility to perform simple mail merge using the LaTeX letter style.
Simply requires a letter in .tex format and a file of addresses.  Each of
these is inserted, in turn, into the .tex file which is run through LaTeX
and then through the printer driver.  Includes C source.  
